SAYRE v. SMITH et al. Where there are no assignment of errors, the appeal will be dismissed. Appeal from the County Court of Yuba County.

W. P. Wilkins for Appellant.

L. F. Aud, for Respondent.

Terry, C. J., at the April Term, 1858, delivered the opinion of the Court

Burnett, J., concurring.

Appeal dismissed for want of assignment of errors.
